title: When does the Zelda: Symphony of the Goddesses tour return to London?
text:
Wednesday, Oct 14 2015, 03:02   Twitter Share on Google+ Zelda fans in the UK will get another chance to experience The Legend of Zelda: Symphony of the Goddesses .The Zelda -themed music tour is officially returning to London for a show on April 23, 2016 at Wembley's SSE Arena. 
Â© Nintendo Although it is still a few months away, you can secure your tickets to the upcoming event right now via AXS.com .Featuring music and visuals from the recently-remastered Majora's Mask 3D and the addition of A Link Between Worlds , the concert series aims to maintain the experience fans encounter while playing Zelda games.It also features live orchestral performances of theme music from Nintendo 's long-running franchise.
